 Macronet structure.
---------------------

TRANSITIONS
T1: MP101 * MP102 |- @MP101 * @MP102;

MACROPLACE 101
    Internal places      : P1,P2,P3
    Internal transitions : T3,T2
    Border transitions   : T1

MACROPLACE 102
    Internal places      : P4,P5,P6
    Internal transitions : T5,T4
    Border transitions   : T1

